strings: <voice_0x01000F25><se_low>*: It's not a lot! His Highness looked delighted. how do you get started?
<voice_0x01000F26><se_def>The prince Carlos: Ah, this is just a formality! sound! I want big things but I'm too busy to waste my time on fancy stuff!
<voice_0x01000F27><se_low>*: Obviously...! This is the biggest heart nut. Did you kill the lizard that eats everyone?
